content:
Automatically runs webpack bundle analyzer when configuration or main entry files change. Generates an interactive treemap visualization of bundle contents to identify optimization opportunities.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *webpack.config.js ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *src/index.js ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *src/main.js ]]; then echo 'ðŸ“Š Analyzing webpack bundle...' && npx webpack-bundle-analyzer ./dist/stats.json ./dist --mode static --report bundle-report.html --no-open 2>/dev/null && echo 'âœ… Bundle analysis saved to bundle-report.html' || (npx webpack --profile --json > ./dist/stats.json && echo 'ðŸ“ˆ Stats generated in dist/stats.json'); fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
